=== IFAS-popular posts by views ===
Tags: popular, view
Requires at least: 4.6.1
Tested up to: 4.7
License: none

This plugin counts views of each post and shows 3 most popular posts (most viewed) on side bar.

== Installation ==
1. Upload the plugin files to the `/wp-content/plugins/plugin-name` directory, or install the plugin through the WordPress plugins screen directly.
2. Activate the plugin through the \'Plugins\' screen in WordPress.
3. Go to Appearance->Widgets panel, there is a new widget named  IFAS Popular Post, add this widget to your blog page.


== Frequently Asked Questions ==
= Get \"HEADERS ALREADY SENT\" error message =

This message randomly appears and it seems to be a part of a theme issue. 